data.title: STA: Anton Rop New Prime Minister Designate
data.meta_description: The outgoing Finance Minister Anton Rop has been appointed Slovenia's new prime minister designate by the parliament. In a secret ballot, he was given a green light in a vote 63 against 24.
data.text: Ljubljana, 11 December - The outgoing Finance Minister Anton Rop has been appointed Slovenia's new prime minister designate by the parliament. In a secret ballot, he was given a green light in a vote 63 against 24.
